Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:51.72,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,700)\b1\pos(522,814)}少年们的逃避之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学四年级的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.57,0:00:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在游泳课上因为没有游完25米
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.09,0:00:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着游泳裤逃到了隔壁镇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的行为似乎是所谓的逃跑癖一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌像你这样的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.19,0:00:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全没意识到你讨厌我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这次我又逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岬姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千仓桑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楠田君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么模仿我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我成为你们的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还真是个超级差劲的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楠田君可不是差劲的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样的人 真不知道什么时候能回复过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的话 明明知道自己想要什么 却不能改变现状
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加 怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:01:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要去遥远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这当然是不可能的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是旅行啊 楠田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我们的再生而进行的旅游
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了发现自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在去 马上去 曾我部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要准备 出发就在明天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家长起床前出发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先准备必要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是食物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 莫非这意思是我也要参加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财津 如果现在不去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定我们以后都无法振作起来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是坐电车 住旅馆之类的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋啊 移动手段是自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上当然是露宿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来必需品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙刷套件也是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备两条短裤就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公园里可以洗衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡要怎么办 洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡是必须的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合时间是明早5点半
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点是四条国道的十字路口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财津若是不想来的话 不来也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们会去 为了改变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果决定要来的话 记得给家里留个条
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个晚上 我考虑好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请不要来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是为了重视自我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我到底想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾我部想变成不同的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财津想脱离失恋军团
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想从那里逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要自信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在几点 楠田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5点42分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财津果然不来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是再稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直找不到家里的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你们想丢下我去旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有考虑过吗 曾我部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又不是我做主的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 诞生的方位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么朝着朝阳比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑那么快很危险的 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡贯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居渡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今天的缺席者是楠田 曾我部 财津三人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑了不少距离呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家肚子不饿吗 因为我没吃早饭就出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我也有点饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火头军班长曾我部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之一人一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的食物就这些零食吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很美味啊 而且挺廉价的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且自行车后备箱里还有行李啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的枕头 用了十年的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我很敏感 所以一旦换了枕头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对曾我部来讲 食物还没有枕头重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就是没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开会 现在开始紧急会议
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在大家带了多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:08:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带了300日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财津怎么了呀 感冒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在一直 嗯 嗯 地痛苦呻吟着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人一起缺席还真是少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定他们一起出去玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是装病
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财津一直对山本的事感到很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装病去玩 绝对不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌像你这样的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 小慧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 没有在听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家打算等下去探望财津
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果三个人加起来 就只有2000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零食还剩下24条
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假设我们出去3天的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我错了 不要生气了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不是更有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.89,0:10:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一点计划性都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}真是的 头痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旅行就可以看见本性了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁是想出来的事 这种事最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要闷闷不乐在那里发牢骚了 出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 楠田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑这么快的话 肚子又要饿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探病 还真是紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望财津君没什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小慧 还是顺便也去楠田君家看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 只要去看财津君就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去又没什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到财津君的家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兽君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫 卫 卫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财津君怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给担心我的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个容易消沉的没用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这样的自己感到厌烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以去旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财津 卫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.12,0:11:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然像是离家出走的信 莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 财津君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 下面好像还写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟曾我部和楠田一点关系都没有 请见谅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就是说 是和那两人一起行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,99.9%是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试试给楠田打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的人 我是最讨厌的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 江之本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江之本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小慧 借我下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似我们走错路了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没办法的呀 照那样走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会进入高速公路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里到底是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我在看地图啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.23,0:13:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楠田君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 那边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是我啊 是我 现在你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁带了指南针了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财津君也在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了 这到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是广播
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始播送
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始野猪养殖馆的野猪赛跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时出售猪汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎各位邀好友一同参加
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在听吗 楠田君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 你是有原吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在讲什么 怎么还带电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是离家出走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楠田赶快挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财津 财津君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家把电话关了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 已经连接不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像把电源关了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是村内广播之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们怎么跑偏僻的乡下去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千仓酱知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和之前同家人一起去旅行 那地方听到的内容一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是仓国温泉附近的村落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那三个人都在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫那家伙 为什么要去那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小慧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小慧 大家一起去把他们找回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 你不担心楠田君吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心吗 小慧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为楠田讨厌我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么呢 你们关系不是很好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 被楠田说了 最讨厌 的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被最讨厌的人跟在后面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很困扰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被讨厌 也有想要传达给他的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样迟疑不决的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的认为不把自己的想法说出来也可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道结果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起什么都不说地活着会好得多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被讨厌 也想传达给他的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还什么都没和那家伙说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是到 温泉的路线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及确认附近的铁路线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是他们的移动工具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说起来 今天早上 卫的自行车就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上他们肯定休息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能预测到他们明天的线路 并且绕前的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对能够追上他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家先回家准备一下 一小时后在车站前集中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去把那群笨蛋给找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土桥也一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.10,0:17:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个眼镜君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让他担心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江之本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兽君 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兽君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要开始做搜寻准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪汁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的东西也没办法 放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问到路了 东边在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 两个人都一言不发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪汁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说有猪汁的 才特地绕远路过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小慧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小慧来讲是不是来得太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点坐不住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次把她叫出来一起去哪里玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你交往的人多得是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那家伙交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊 我只对有原君有感觉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫离家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}他们的位置已经确定了 步美她们已经去了 我也准备出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有要事的话 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 不用我出场的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有原 一直找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没看见我妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宵那家伙 留下这个就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和步美一起 所以不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美也一起啊 那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心是肯定的吧 笨蛋 去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有原对我没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么尽是上坡路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真啰嗦 找不到过夜的地方 没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楠田君 这样大吼大叫的话体力消耗会更加厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 照这个趋势在我们重生之前就先饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了 大吼大叫的话肚子会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楠田他们 现在可能在泡温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 小宵 为什么会一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是明摆着 因为很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 他们到底打算去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么野猪会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.73,0:21:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快骑 玩命地骑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楠田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小慧 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:21:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是野猪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:22:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楠田
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.23,0:22:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停车 快把火车停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:59.95,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FFFFFF\pos(490,814)}初恋限定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.14,0:23:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从开始喜欢财津君后开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.56,0:23:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的初恋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.67,0:23:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也差不多该有答案了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财津君和野兽君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.14,0:23:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底何去何从

